    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In dei nomine amen. Anno nativitatis eius millesimo centesimo nonagesimo
                        septimo, tertiodecimo kal. augusti, indictione quintadecima. Ex hoc publico
                        instrumento omnibus elucescat quod nos, <persName><name ref="Martinus"
                                >Martinus</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Ammannatus"
                                >Ammannatus</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Natalis"
                                >Natale</name></persName> germani quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Bonafides">Bonafidei</name></persName>, nos tres simul vendimus
                        et tradimus tibi <persName><name ref="Pierus">Piero</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Signorectus">Signorecti</name></persName> unam
                        nostram petiam de terra in finibus Montis Falconi, posita ad Ortum Pulcelle,
                        quod tenet unum caput in terra <persName><name ref="Palmaris"
                            >Palmari</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Damianus"
                                >Dammiani</name></persName>, aliud in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Ciaffarinus">Ciaffarini</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName>, latus unum in
                        terra filiorum quondam <persName><name ref="Rodelandus"
                            >Orlandi</name></persName> et suprascripti Ciaffarini, aliud vero latus
                        in terra <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2041"><rs
                                key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> Sancti Quirici</orgName>. (…)
                            <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: libris tribus soldis quinque bonorum
                        denariorum pisani. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum. (…) Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/3202">Monti Falconis</placeName> (…) presentibus <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Menculus">Menculo</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Bacalare">Bacalari</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Leulus">Leulo</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Baro">Barone</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Amadeus">Amateo</name></persName> et
                        aliis ad hec rogatis <rs key="#Witness">testibus</rs>. (S) <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Lanfrancus"
                            >Lannfrancus</name></persName> domini regis Henrigi <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notarius</rs> omnia suprascripta mea proria manu publicis litteris
                        scripsi, complevi et dedi.</ab>
